UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2586
1 Be it resolved by the House of Representatives of the General Assembly of the
2 Commonwealth of Kentucky:
3 Section 1. The House of Representatives hereby designates May 2026 as Save
4 Your Tooth Month, acknowledges endodontists as leaders dedicated to saving patients'
5 natural teeth, and encourages the citizens of Kentucky to practice good oral hygiene to
6 save their natural teeth.
7 Section 2. The Clerk of the House of Representatives is directed to transmit a
8 copy of this Resolution to Representative Lindsey Burke for delivery.
